'''阿祖安·聖米基爾·迪·卡斯迪路'''（{{lang-es|Adrián San Miguel Del Castillo}}，{{bd|1987年|1月3日|catIdx=Adrián}}）是一名[[西班牙|西班牙]]足球运动员，司职[[守門員|守門員]]，目前效力于[[英超|英超]]球隊[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]。

== 俱樂部生涯 ==
[[File:Adrian_2013_001.jpg|thumb]]
===貝迪斯===
阿祖安出生於[[安達盧西亞|安達盧西亞]]的[[西維爾|西維爾]]，他自小在11歲以下隊伍CD Altair司職[[前鋒|前鋒]]或[[邊鋒|邊鋒]]，直到10歲時因為當時的門將離開球會，阿祖安才轉踢守門員<ref name="CD Altair">{{cite news | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/west-ham/11346888/West-Ham-United-cult-hero-Adrian-in-frame-for-Spain-following-FA-Cup-heroics-against-Everton-at-Upton-Park.html | title=West Ham United cult-hero Adrian in frame for Spain following FA Cup heroics against Everton at Upton Park | work=The Telegraph | date=14 January 2015 | accessdate=4 April 2015 | author=Wilson, Jeremy | archive-date=2020-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029184253/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/west-ham/11346888/West-Ham-United-cult-hero-Adrian-in-frame-for-Spain-following-FA-Cup-heroics-against-Everton-at-Upton-Park.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。後來，他其後加入貝迪斯少年軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eldesmarque.com/betis/48197-la-historia-de-adrian-el-portero-que-empezo-de-delantero-video|title=La historia de Adrián, el portero que empezó de delantero (vídeo)|trans_title=The story of Adrián, the goalkeeper who started as a forward (video)|publisher=El Desmarque|language=es|accessdate=12 October 2012|date=6 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928013212/http://www.eldesmarque.com/betis/48197-la-historia-de-adrian-el-portero-que-empezo-de-delantero-video|archive-date=2013-09-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在C隊內渡過兩個賽季，其後五季在預備組效力，當中四個球季在[[西班牙足球乙二級聯賽|西乙二]]比賽，但是只是後備門將<ref>[http://www.estadiodeportivo.com/betis.php?pg=2&id=33629 Con Adrián, el Betis está en buenas manos (With Adrián, Betis is in good hands)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929045811/http://www.estadiodeportivo.com/betis.php?pg=2&id=33629 |date=2013-09-29 }}; Estadio Deportivo, 24 October 2012 {{es icon}}</ref>。他還在2008年被借到CD Alcalá及在2009年被借到CD Utrera<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whufc.com/Teams/First-Team/Squad/Adrian|title=Adrian|publisher=West Ham United|accessdate=3 April 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501112833/http://www.whufc.com/Teams/First-Team/Squad/Adrian|archivedate=2015年5月1日|df=}}</ref><ref name="aleja">{{cite web|url=http://mercafichajes.es/06/04/2013/adrian-aleja-betis/|title=Adrián se aleja del Betis|trans_title=Adrián moves away from Betis|publisher=MercaFichajes|language=es|date=6 April 2013|accessdate=3 April 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005202225/http://mercafichajes.es/06/04/2013/adrian-aleja-betis/|archive-date=2017-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2011-12賽季，他被提升至貝迪斯一隊作為第三門將選擇，而且仍繼續出現在貝迪斯B隊。2011年11月，他的十字[[韌帶|韌帶]]遭受了嚴重傷害因而被迫缺陣五個半月<ref name="442interview">{{cite web | url=http://www.fourfourtwo.com/features/adrian-allardyce-great-manager-he-only-speaks-holiday-spanish | title=Adrian: Allardyce is a great manager - but he only speaks 'holiday Spanish'! | publisher=www.fourfourtwo.com | accessdate=4 April 2015 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006013140/https://www.fourfourtwo.com/features/adrian-allardyce-great-manager-he-only-speaks-holiday-spanish | archive-date=2017-10-06 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.diariodesevilla.es/article/realbetis/1110680/portero/adriaacuten/estaraacute/baja/medio/antildeo/por/una/lesioacuten/rodilla.html El portero Adrián estará de baja medio año por una lesión de rodilla (Goalkeeper Adrián will miss half a year due to knee injury)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.diariodesevilla.es/article/realbetis/1110680/portero/adriaacuten/estaraacute/baja/medio/antildeo/por/una/lesioacuten/rodilla.html |date=20160816021353 }}; Diario de Sevilla, 10 November 2011 {{es icon}}</ref>。

阿祖安在2012年9月29日終於首次在[[西甲|西甲]]亮相，但是該場以0-4作客敗於[[馬拉加足球會|馬拉加]]，因為當時正選門將[[卡斯圖_(足球運動員)|卡斯圖]]在開賽早段被罰出場，阿祖安取代了在場球員[[薩爾瓦多·阿格拉|薩爾瓦多·阿格拉]]，他被評為本場最佳球員<ref name=442interview/><ref>[http://espnfc.com/uk/en/report/348458/report.html?soccernet=true&cc=5739 Malaga crush 10-man Betis] {{Wayback|url=http://espnfc.com/uk/en/report/348458/report.html?soccernet=true&cc=5739 |date=20140418003004 }}; ESPN Soccernet, 29 September 2012</ref>。在2012-13賽季，他成為了首席門將，最令人囑目的比賽表現是於2012年11月24日在對陣[[皇馬|皇馬]]時以1-0主場取勝<ref>[http://soccernet.espn.go.com/report?id=348394&cc=5739 Betis stun Real Madrid]{{Dead link}}; ESPN Soccernet, 24 November 2012</ref>。在首次上陣後他繼續有出色的表現，在其後的31場比賽中，保持了11場沒有失球，並帶領貝迪斯以第七位完成西甲聯賽及取得出席[[歐霸盃|歐霸盃]]資格<ref name=whusign/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deportes.elpais.com/deportes/2013/04/19/actualidad/1366393799_979093.html|title=Diego López se lo ha ganado|trans_title=Diego López has done very well for himself|publisher=[[國家報|國家報]]|language=es|date=19 April 2013|accessdate=6 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602222332/http://deportes.elpais.com/deportes/2013/04/19/actualidad/1366393799_979093.html|archive-date=2017-06-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

===韋斯咸===
當韋斯咸領隊[[森姆·艾拿戴斯|艾拿戴斯]]和守門員教練觀看了阿祖安在貝迪斯出色的表現後，阿祖安被說服加入韋斯咸<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.london24.com/sport/football/clubs/west-ham/allardyce_reveals_how_spain_trip_convinced_adrian_to_join_west_ham_1_3345875 | title=Allardyce reveals how Spain trip convinced Adrian to join West Ham | publisher=www.london24.com | date=22 February 2014 | accessdate=4 April 2015 | author=Wright, Nick | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409061130/http://www.london24.com/sport/football/clubs/west-ham/allardyce_reveals_how_spain_trip_convinced_adrian_to_join_west_ham_1_3345875 | archivedate=2015-04-09}}</ref>。2013年6月5日，宣佈阿祖安將於7月1日加盟韋斯咸，簽約為期三年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11685/8758851/West-Ham-secure-the-signing-of-Spanish-keeper-Adrian|title=West Ham secure the signing of Spanish keeper Adrian|publisher=[[天空體育台|天空體育台]]|date=5 June 2013|accessdate=5 June 2013|archive-date=2014-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029041430/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11685/8758851/West-Ham-secure-the-signing-of-Spanish-keeper-Adrian|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該英超球會更有權選擇延長該合約多兩個賽季<ref name="whusign">{{cite web|url=http://www.whufc.com/articles/20130605/hammers-catch-goalkeeper-adrian_2236884_3201244|title=Hammers catch keeper Adrian|publisher=West Ham United|date=5 June 2013|accessdate=6 June 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609082407/http://www.whufc.com/articles/20130605/hammers-catch-goalkeeper-adrian_2236884_3201244|archivedate=2013-06-09}}</ref>。

阿祖安於2013年8月27日在該賽季的聯賽杯賽事首次為韋斯咸上陣以2-1主場贏了[[車頓咸足球會|車頓咸]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sport.co.uk/football/west-ham-21-cheltenham-match-report/4383702/|title=West Ham 2–1 Cheltenham: Match report|publisher=Sport.co|date=27 August 2013|accessdate=29 August 2013|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726044455/https://www.sport.co.uk/football/west-ham-21-cheltenham-match-report/4383702/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在比賽期間，他因侵犯對方球員是使其获得一個十二碼，被對方射入。他的首場英超聯賽是在2013年12月21日，當日韋斯咸以1-3輸給[[曼聯|曼聯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espnfc.com/uk/en/report/367335/report.html|title=United revival gathering pace|publisher=ESPN FC|date=21 December 2013|accessdate=22 December 2013|archive-date=2013-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131226072557/http://espnfc.com/uk/en/report/367335/report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年1月11日阿祖安保持了他的第一場英超不失球，在客場以2：0擊敗[[卡迪夫城|卡迪夫城]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ftbpro.com/posts/paul.websell/616310/jussi-or-adrian-who-should-be-west-ham-s-number-one|title=Jussi or Adrian: Who should be West Ham's number one?|publisher=FTB Pro|author=Websell, Paul|date=15 January 2014|accessdate=9 February 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222064714/http://www.ftbpro.com/posts/paul.websell/616310/jussi-or-adrian-who-should-be-west-ham-s-number-one|archivedate=2014-02-22}}</ref>。同年5月6日，他參加了球會的獎項頒獎，並以2014年1月對陣[[車路士|車路士]]的賽事中救出[[奧斯卡·杜斯山度士·艾保亞巴·祖利亞|奧斯卡]]的撲救榮獲“該賽季最佳撲救”。他還在同一場比賽中獲得了“最佳個人表現”，他保持不失球而互交白卷，以及成為“該賽季的最佳收購球員”;他還被評為當年度最佳韋斯咸球員亞軍，敗於[[馬克·盧保|馬克·盧保]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whufc.com/articles/20140506/201314-player-awards-live_2236884_3809162|title=Noble is Hammer of the Year|publisher=West Ham United|date=6 May 2014|accessdate=6 May 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140506221620/http://www.whufc.com/articles/20140506/201314-player-awards-live_2236884_3809162|archivedate=2014-05-06}}</ref>。到了2013-14賽季，他已經取代了取代了[[尤西·積亞基連倫|積亞基連倫]]成為韋斯咸的正選門將<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27697033 | title=Jussi Jaaskelainen: West Ham goalkeeper signs new contract | publisher=BBC體育 | date=4 June 2014 | accessdate=4 April 2015 | archive-date=2015-12-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224044521/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27697033 | dead-url=no }}</ref>
。

在該賽季在2015年1月13日的足總杯第三輪重賽，對陣愛華頓的[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]時，阿祖安救出了[[史堤芬·尼史密夫|史堤芬·尼史密夫]]的十二碼球。互射十二碼進入突然死亡階段，對方守門員[[若埃爾·羅伯斯|若埃爾·羅伯斯]]的十二碼球擊中門框<ref>{{cite news|last1=Emons|first1=Michael|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30705802|title=West Ham 2–2 Everton|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC體育]]|date=13 January 2015|accessdate=14 January 2015|archive-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416202605/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30705802|dead-url=no}}</ref>，儘管有之前從來沒有在正式比賽射入十二碼球，阿祖安非常有信心會入球並贏得該場比賽，他射十二碼球前脫下守門員手套，阿祖安射入最後一輪十二碼球，並為他的球隊以9-8贏了該場比賽<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30808244|title=Adrian: West Ham keeper knew he would score FA Cup penalty|publisher=BBC體育|date=13 January 2015|accessdate=14 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150118034244/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30808244|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年2月11日，阿祖安在對[[修咸頓足球會|修咸頓]]的賽事中因在對手的力壓下於禁區外用手接球而被出示紅牌直接被趕出場，該場賽事雙方互交白卷<ref>{{cite news|last1=Reddy|first1=Luke|title=Southampton 0–0 West Ham|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31124632|accessdate=13 February 2015|work=BBC體育|date=11 February 2015|archive-date=2015-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309103915/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31124632|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然韋斯咸在該場賽事被控未能控制自己的球員，但是阿祖安在被逐後的停賽被[[英格蘭足球總會|英國足總]]取消<ref>{{cite news|title=Adrian: West Ham keeper's red card overturned, but club charged|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31459377|accessdate=13 February 2015|work=BBC體育|date=13 February 2015|archive-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306085540/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31459377|dead-url=no}}</ref>。韋斯咸亦因此被罰款30000英鎊<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31559332 | title=West Ham fined by the FA for failing to control players | publisher=BBC體育 | accessdate=4 April 2015 | archive-date=2015-05-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520084945/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31559332 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===利物浦===
2019年8月5日，阿祖安以自由身加盟[[英超|英超]]球隊[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]。

2019年8月10日，19-20賽季[[英超|英超]]揭幕戰主場對[[諾域治城足球會|諾域治]]的比賽中，阿祖安在39分鐘時後備入替受傷的[[阿利森·拉姆西斯·贝克尔|艾利臣]]，首次代表球隊出戰，並以4-1獲勝。

2019年8月14日，[[2019年歐洲超級盃|欧洲超级杯]]比赛上，阿德里安首次代表利物浦首发出场，并于[[点球大战|点球大战]]中扑出[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切尔西]]前锋[[塔米·亚伯拉罕|阿巴謙]]的点球，帮助球队以7-6的总比分夺得冠军。

